---
title: Pate of the Blue Fork
---

Ser Pate, better known as Ser Pate of the Blue Fork also known as Ser Pate of Sevenstreams, was a hedge knight from the Riverlands. He was married to Amerei Frey, the eldest daughter of Merrett Frey. He was killed by Ser Gregor Clegane. He was a cousin of Tom of Sevenstreams, who sang at his wedding. 


